#: 21337012-0-377
msgctxt "21337012-0-377"
msgid "Kyne, one of the Eight Divines of the Nord pantheon, is considered by some to lead those Divines. She is one of the Hearth Gods, watching over the present cycle of the world. Her titles are numerous, revealing much about the character of Kyne."
"\n"
"\nKyne is called the Kiss at the End, for most Nords agree that Kyne leads the dead to Sovngarde. She is revered as the Goddess of Storm, called upon to bring rain and snow in dry times. She protects her faithful from the raging gales and blizzards that regularly sweep across the Skyrim expanse. Other names applied to Kyne include Widow of Shor and the Mother of Nords."
"\n"
"\nWarriors favor Kyne, as they call upon her for strength in battle and victory in conflict."
msgstr ""

#: 51188213-0-377
msgctxt "51188213-0-377"
msgid "Goddess of Storm, Mother of Nords"
msgstr ""

#: 21337012-0-351
msgctxt "21337012-0-351"
msgid "By Denskar"
"\n"
"\nBeen thinking about our fight against the Akaviri. I've got opinions. Think I'll write them down. "
"\n"
"\nThe whole damned war could have been avoided if those idiots in Windhelm had the sense to throw the Snakes back into the sea. Shor take them!"
"\n"
"\nStill wish Jorunn had moved to reinforce Windhelm. Lost some good men that day."
"\n"
"\nJorunn fortified Riften, but the Snakes rolled right past. Why go straight to the Ashlands?"
"\n"
"\nThe fighting south of Riften, north of Fort Virak, isn't given enough respect. Those men were pinned and outmanned, and still they held."
"\n"
"\nWulfharth was the only reason the men kept fighting that day. Jorunn was just a pup. He couldn't rally a mead hall."
"\n"
"\nThe Snakes push into Stonefalls after the fall of Fort Virak. Why? What were they after?"
"\n"
"\nHeard rumors some of the Dark Elves turned their blades on the Shellbacks at first. Couldn't stand the thought of being rescued by Argonians. Damned fools."
"\n"
"\nShor take the whole Snake island. Let them send another tiger demon! We'll take them again!"
msgstr "덴스카 씀"
"\n"
"\n우리가 아카비리와 맞서 싸웠던 일에 대해 지금까지 생각해 왔다. 내게 생각이 있다. 내가 아래에 쓸 생각 말이다."
"\n"
"\n그 빌어먹을 모든 전쟁은 윈드헬름의 멍청이들이 뱀들을 다시 바다로 던져넣을 생각만 했더라도 피할 수 있었던 것이었다. 쇼어께서 놈들을 잡아가시길!"
"\n"
"\n지금도 요룬이 윈드헬름을 보강하러 떠났으면 좋았을 것이라고 생각한다. 좋은 사람 몇 명을 그날 잃었다."
"\n"
"\n요룬은 리프튼을 요새화했지만, 뱀들은 그곳을 바로 우회해 지나쳤다. 왜 곧장 재의 땅으로 갔을까?"
"\n"
"\n리프튼 남부와 비락 요새 북부에서의 싸움은 마땅히 받아야 할 존중을 받지 못했다. 거기서 싸웠던 사람들은 꼼짝 못한 채 숫적으로 밀렸던 상태였고, 아직까지도 고립되어 있다."
"\n"
"\n그날 우리가 계속 싸웠던 이유는 오직 울프하스 때문이었다. 요룬은 애송이일 뿐이었다. 요룬은 미드 홀을 집결시킬 수 없었다."
"\n"
"\n뱀들은 비락 요새 함락 후에 스톤폴스로 밀고 나갔다. 왜일까? 무엇을 노린 것일까?"
"\n"
"\n들리는 소문으로는 처음엔 다크 엘프 몇 명이 놈들의 검을 Shellback들에게로 돌렸다고 한다. 아르고니안에게 구출된다는 생각을 견딜 수 가 없었던 것이다. 망할 바보놈들."
"\n"
"\n쇼어께서 뱀들의 섬을 전부 잡아가시길. 호랑이 악마들을 보내라고 해라! 우린 다시 이겨낼 수 있다!"

